    // (Huang et al., Energies 11(9):2419, 2018 — also Rosano-Maniktala
    // "Power Supplies A to Z" 3rd ed.):
    //   D1 = primary-bridge intra-leg shift
    //   D2 = secondary-bridge intra-leg shift
